snippet.title: Open Hexagon - 60+ Seconds on All Levels
snippet.description:
For when Super Hexagon isn't hard enough.

You can't really "beat" a level in Open Hexagon, just set a high score. Because of that, I made my goal to get 60+ seconds on everything that comes with the game (no user-created levels).

Pointless - 0:03
Flattering Shape - 2:35
Second Dimension - 4:10
Apeirogon - 5:26
Euclidean Plane Crash - 6:51
Pi - 8:10
Golden Ratio - 9:24
Commando - 10:39
Labyrinth - 11:46
Acceleradiant - 12:50
Incongruence - 13:59
Polyhedrug - 15:13
